      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "张从"
      ],
      "text": "嗯哼！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00006",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "强盗甲"
      ],
      "text": "那旁有人来了，你我闪在一旁。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00007",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二强盗自下场门同下。张从自上场门上。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00008",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张从"
      ],
      "text": "一日离家一日深，好似孤雁宿寒林。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00009",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张从"
      ],
      "text": "在下张从，乃湖广长沙人氏。奉了双亲之命，上京贸易，看今日天气晴和，赶路要紧。",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00010",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张从"
      ],
      "text": "不分昼夜往前进，急忙回家奉双亲。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00011",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二强盗同上，同杀张从。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00012",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "强盗甲"
      ],
      "text": "你我将包裹分了吧。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00013",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二强盗同分包裹，同争一枚金钱。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
