      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二强盗同下。二路人同上。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00017",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "四平调",
      "speakers": [
        "老路人"
      ],
      "text": "我家有棵摇钱树！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00018",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "少路人"
      ],
      "text": "得了，你们家哪儿有摇钱树啊，别犯财迷啦！",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00019",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老路人"
      ],
      "text": "你哪里知道，我家有一个果木树，等它结了果，卖了钱，岂不与摇钱树一样！",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00020",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "少路人"
      ],
      "text": "那么说，我也有啊！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00021",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老路人"
      ],
      "text": "你有什么啊？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00022",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "少路人"
      ],
      "text": "你听着啊！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00023",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "四平调",
      "speakers": [
        "少路人"
      ],
      "text": "我家里有个聚宝盆。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00024",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老路人"
      ],
      "text": "你们家，哪里来的聚宝盆？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00025",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "少路人"
      ],
      "text": "我家养活了一个老母猪，等它下了小猪，卖了钱，岂不是聚宝盆么！",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00026",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老路人"
      ],
      "text": "你别净犯财迷了！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00027",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "少路人"
      ],
      "text": "得啦！你看那边是个什么？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00028",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老路人"
      ],
      "text": "待我看来。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00029",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "老路人看。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00030",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老路人"
      ],
      "text": "原来是一死尸，口内还有一枚金钱。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00031",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "少路人"
      ],
      "text": "咱们敲出来，咱们俩人分呐？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00032",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老路人"
      ],
      "text": "如此就敲起来！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00033",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二路人同敲。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00034",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "无量佛！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00035",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "庄周上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00036",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄散板",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "大路旁边一古刹，七岁儿童讲道法。幼童尚知修行好，何况庄周是道家。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00037",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "庄周看。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00038",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "啊？老丈，你们在此做甚？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00039",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老路人"
      ],
      "text": "我们这里敲骨求金呐。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00040",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，我想世界之上，只有求金葬骨，哪有敲骨求金之理，依贫道相劝，你们不要敲了。",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00041",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老路人"
      ],
      "text": "他不叫咱敲，跟他要一枚金钱，咱们就不敲。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00042",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "你且少待。哎呀，且住！他们与我要一枚金钱，方肯不敲，这便如何是好？哦，有了！师父教我点石成金之术，待我试来！“天灵灵，地灵灵，石块变成金！”呵，果有一枚金钱。老丈拿了去，你们不必敲了。",
      "text_length": 92
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00043",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "老路人接金。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00044",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "少路人"
      ],
      "text": "这个老道，是个傻子。咱们还是敲，他要不教敲，咱们跟他要十枚金钱。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00045",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老路人"
      ],
      "text": "如此敲起来。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00046",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "啊，老丈，你们怎么又敲起来了？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00047",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老路人"
      ],
      "text": "你要不教我们敲，得给我们十枚金钱。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00048",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "请少待。哎呀且住。看他贪得无厌，我不免谴动神虎，惊散他们。“天灵灵，地灵灵，神虎速降！”",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00049",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "虎形上，二路人同跑下。庄周笑。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00050",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "谴动神虎下山来，张牙舞爪把头抬。老者见了魂不在，少了见了哭悲哀。放神虎回仙界！",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00051",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "庄周看虎形，虎形对张从做咬状。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00052",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "胆大孽畜，还不归山。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00053",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "虎形下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00054",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄散板",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "见一尸骨倒尘埃。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00055",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "那旁有一死尸，待我掐指算来。此人姓张名从字骷髅，乃湖广长沙人氏，奉了双亲之命，上京贸易，被二强人杀死，想我出家之人，焉有见死不救之理，师父赐我阴阳宝扇，不免救活与他。",
      "text_length": 83
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00056",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "张从生来只爱财！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00057",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄散板",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "谁知一命赴阴台。用手打开皮囊袋，救你一命转回来。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00058",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "庄周看。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00059",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀且住！只因他生前欠下猛虎命债，今神虎衔去喀骨三根，我不免搬动树枝，与他接骨便了。",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00060",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "忙将树枝来搬动，接骨救命小张从。腹中无有心肝肺，枉教贫道把善行。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00061",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "又无心肝，如何是好？呵！有了！山下来了一只黄犬，我将它杀死，用它心肝救活张从便了。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00062",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "犬形上，庄周打倒犬形。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00063",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "将犬打倒地埃尘，手持戒刀下无情。犬心救活张从命，为救一命又害一生。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00064",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀且住！为救一人，害了一犬，背了上天好生之德，如何是好？呵！有了！不免用土作成犬心，救活与它！",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00065",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "黄土作成了犬的心，人心怎比你的心。阴阳宝扇救活了你！",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00066",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "犬形下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00067",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "摆尾摇头下山林。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00068",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "庄周取扇，扇张从。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00069",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "一扇君子把头抬，二扇君子眼睁开；三扇君子四体摆，活来活去你快活来！",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00070",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀且住！我既将他救活，他醒来，若向我要他的行囊包裹，如何是好？呵！有了，我且在此打坐，他有来言，我有去语。",
      "text_length": 54
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00071",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "张从"
      ],
      "text": "霎时间一阵阵昏迷不醒，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00072",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄散板",
      "speakers": [
        "张从"
      ],
      "text": "不见包裹为何情？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00073",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 73,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张从"
      ],
      "text": "适才我觉得一阵昏迷，醒来为何行囊包裹，俱已不见！",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00074",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 74,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "嗯哼！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00075",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 75,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张从"
      ],
      "text": "那旁有一道者，想是被他盗去，待我向他要来。呃！那一道者，你在此打坐，可曾见我行囊包裹？",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00076",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 76,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "贫道在此打坐，未曾见你行囊包裹。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00077",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 77,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张从"
      ],
      "text": "此处四下无人，想是被你偷了去了。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00078",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 78,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "出家人不爱财，爱财就不出家。想是你打睡之时，行囊包裹被旁人盗去，不要诬赖贫道。",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00079",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 79,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张从"
      ],
      "text": "你不还我，我要告你！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00080",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 80,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "哪里去告？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00081",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 81,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张从"
      ],
      "text": "南华县去告。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00082",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 82,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "你且少待。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00083",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 83,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "庄周背躬。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00084",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 84,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀且住！闻得南华县令，爱民如子，人品非凡，不免借此会他一会。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00085",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 85,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "庄周对张从。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00086",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 86,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "君子你饶恕了贫道吧。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00087",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 87,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张从"
      ],
      "text": "不能饶你！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00088",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 88,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄周"
      ],
      "text": "这是哪里说起！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13001007_e00089",
      "play_id": "13001007",
      "scene_id": "13001007_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 89,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "庄周、张从同下。",
      "text_length": 8
    }
  ],
